I realise it's not the best recording, because of the background noise.

However, it is a proud one for me and Iracambi, as it is the first recording of which the bird was identified. We are 95% certain of it being the Little Tinamou, as the frequency and length of the call are exactly the same as reference sounds on Xeno Canto and Ebird.
